{"tid":1802242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（不能只有我看到）佔港共軍聯合訓練片段曝光","createTime":"2019-12-29T10:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T11:45:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"33ee08fa1d0b47f2e2acb4be17801d01c7ed2ebe","tid":1802242,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201912/20191229afs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201912%2F20191229afs.jpg&h=3b0dc676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（12月29日）下午，解放軍駐港部隊上載三軍聯合訓練片段，或許會吸引大家專程觀看他們的官方微博，但大家可能會被另一條片段所吸引。<br />\n<br />\n話說駐港部隊的微博，於聖誕日分享了一個叫「港島奇兵」帳戶上載的片段，該片長18秒的片段見到，3名士兵化身「草蜢」，以維港作背景翩翩起舞。原來《環球時報》的英文版Twitter，亦都上載了這條片段。<br />\n<br />\n微博提到「我們的兵哥哥也有活潑的一面哦」，你又是否同意呢？<br />\n<br />\n（網上片段截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-29-2019/58660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-29-2019%2F58660&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=c4426e3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-29-2019/58660</a>"},{"pid":"4a6997577d0dda9a8fb7e8b8b1ce42b1ddc2ce47","tid":1802242,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:21:21.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd164abe721fcdd0827b0bb176c1a9604f0b8c0d","tid":1802242,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"太監<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}